# UpSurge Design System

All UI work must follow the Nova-grade design language established in this project.

## Stack

- **Framework:** Next.js 14 App Router + Tailwind CSS only (no shadcn/MUI/Chakra)
- **Icons:** `lucide-react` (strokeWidth 1.75)
- **Font:** Inter via `next/font/google` (`--font-inter`)
- **Charts:** `recharts` only when displaying real data (no mock charts)

## Layout

- Authenticated pages use `PageShell` from `@/components/TopNav` (sidebar + top bar + main content)
- Login page is standalone (no `PageShell`)
- Main content max-width: `max-w-6xl`, padding `px-6 py-8`
- Sidebar width: `240px`, fixed left

## Design Tokens (tailwind.config.ts)

- **Background:** `bg-ink-50`, `bg-page-gradient`
- **Cards:** `bg-white`, `rounded-2xl`, `border-ink-200/50`, `shadow-card`
- **Text:** `text-ink-900` (primary), `text-ink-500` (secondary), `text-ink-400` (tertiary)
- **Brand:** `brand-*` blues + `bg-brand-gradient` (blue→green)
- **Accents:** `accent-mint-*`, `accent-sky-*`, `accent-violet-*`, `accent-amber-*`, `accent-rose-*`
- **Shadows:** `shadow-soft`, `shadow-card`, `shadow-lifted`, `shadow-pill`
- **Radii:** `rounded-xl` (inputs/buttons), `rounded-2xl` (cards), `rounded-3xl` (hero elements)

## Components (src/components/ui.tsx)

Always use these primitives — never raw Tailwind for common patterns:

| Component | Use for |
|-----------|---------|
| `Button` | Actions (variants: primary, secondary, danger, ghost; sizes: sm, md, lg) |
| `Input`, `Select`, `Label` | Form fields |
| `Card` | Containers (`hover` prop for clickable cards) |
| `Badge`, `StatusBadge` | Status indicators |
| `IconBadge` | Colored icon in rounded-square (tones: mint, sky, violet, amber, rose) |
| `StatTile` | KPI/metric display |
| `SectionHeader` | Section titles with optional description + action |
| `PageGreeting` | Page title + subtitle |
| `Segmented` | Pill-style toggle groups |
| `Pill` | Selectable tag chips |
| `Tabs` | Tab navigation |
| `EmptyState` | Zero-data states |
| `Skeleton` | Loading placeholders |
| `InsightPanel` | Gradient AI/highlight panels |
| `cn()` | Class merging |

## Page Patterns

1. Wrap authenticated pages in `<PageShell>`
2. Use `PageGreeting` or `SectionHeader` for page/section titles
3. Use `StatTile` + `IconBadge` for metrics
4. Use `Card hover` for clickable list items with `ArrowUpRight` affordance
5. Use `EmptyState` for zero-data, `Skeleton` for loading
6. Back links: `ArrowLeft` icon + muted text, `hover:text-ink-700`
7. Error messages: `bg-accent-rose-bg text-accent-rose-fg rounded-xl`
8. Success messages: `bg-accent-mint-bg text-accent-mint-fg rounded-xl`

## Do NOT

- Add harsh borders (`border-slate-300`) — use `border-ink-200/50` or shadows
- Use `rounded-lg` for cards — cards are `rounded-2xl`
- Use system default font — Inter is required
- Create one-off button/card styles — extend `ui.tsx` instead
- Add mock data visualizations — charts only with real API data
- Change API routes, fetch URLs, state logic, or validation when doing UI work
